---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main>
		<section id="sectionAbout">
			<h1>Mego Studio</h1>
			<span class="badge">Desarrollador Full-Stack</span>
			<h2>Sobre mí</h2>
			<p>
				Hola, soy Diego Mejia un apasionado Desarrollador Web Full-Stack
				trabajando independientemente desarrollando productos web. Estoy
				terminando mi carrera de Ingenieria en Sistemas en la
				U.M.S.S(Universidad Mayor de San Simón)
			</p>
			<p>
				Me enorgullesco de ser proactivo, adaptable, bueno trabahando en equipo,
				compartiendo experiencias y conocimientos. Constantemente me esfuerzo
				por mejorar, aprovecho cada oportunidad para aprender y mejorar mis
				habilidades para entregar buenos resultados.
			</p>
			<div class="center">
				<a href="/en/projects">
					<button class="btn">My portafolio</button>
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="sectionSkills">
			<h2>Habilidades</h2>
			<div class="skills center">
				<img
					id="gitIcon"
					alt="Git icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="Git"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="htmlIcon"
					alt="HTML icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="HTML"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="cssIcon"
					alt="CSS Icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="CSS"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="javascriptIcon"
					alt="Javascript icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="JavaScript"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="typescriptIcon"
					alt="Typescript icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="TypeScript"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/typescript/typescript-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="postgresqlIcon"
					alt="Postgresql icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="PostgreSQL"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="mongodbIcon"
					alt="Mongodb icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="MongoDB"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/mongodb/mongodb-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="tailwindIcon"
					alt="Tailwind icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="TailwindCSS"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="astroIcon"
					alt="Astro icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="Astro"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/astro/astro-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="reactIcon"
					alt="React icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="React"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/react/react-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="nextjsIcon"
					alt="Nextjs icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="NextJS"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/nextjs/nextjs-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="csharpIcon"
					alt="Csharp icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="C#"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/csharp/csharp-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="dotnetcoreIcon"
					alt="Dotnetcore icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title=".NET Core"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/dotnetcore/dotnetcore-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="vercelIcon"
					alt="Vercel icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="Vercel"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/vercel/vercel-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="awsIcon"
					alt="Amazon web services icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="AWS"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/amazonwebservices/amazonwebservices-original-wordmark.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="cloudflareIcon"
					alt="Cloudflare icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="Cloudflare"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/cloudflare/cloudflare-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="dockerIcon"
					alt="Docker icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="Docker"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/docker/docker-original.svg"
				/>
				<img
					id="gcIcon"
					alt="Google cloud icon in skills section"
					class="skills-img"
					title="Google Cloud"
					src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/googlecloud/googlecloud-original.svg"
				/>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="sectionInterests">
			<h2>Intereses</h2>
			<p>
				El mundo de la tecnologia siempre ha llamado mi atencion, pero no he
				dejado de lado el mundo real. Por lo que, ademas de la tecnologia, me
				interesa el senderismo, acampar, anime, arte, baloncesto y otros
				diversos deportes.
			</p>
			<p>
				Actualmente, estoy muy interesado en continuar con el desarrollo web y a
				su vez aprender diseño 3D, animacion y desarrollo de videojuegos.
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
